---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { roadmap } from '../data/site';
---

<BaseLayout title="Roadmap | lys Open Source System">
  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-head page-intro">
      <div>
        <span class="eyebrow">Roadmap</span>
        <h1>接下来会补什么，和你有什么关系。</h1>
        <p>这一页不是内部排期表，而是告诉学习者：后续哪些能力、文章、入口和项目体验会继续变得更完整。</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section-grid">
      <article class="section-card">
        <span class="eyebrow">Theme</span>
        <h2>{roadmap.theme}</h2>
      </article>
      <article class="section-card">
        <span class="eyebrow">Why it matters</span>
        <p>如果你把这个站当成学习入口，那么这里列出的事情，会直接影响你下一次能体验到什么、能读到什么、能继续学到哪里。</p>
      </article>
      <article class="section-card">
        <span class="eyebrow">In Progress</span>
        <ul class="list">
          {roadmap.inProgress.map((item) => <li>{item}</li>)}
        </ul>
      </article>
      <article class="section-card">
        <span class="eyebrow">Planned</span>
        <ul class="list">
          {roadmap.planned.map((item) => <li>{item}</li>)}
        </ul>
      </article>
      <article class="section-card">
        <span class="eyebrow">Done</span>
        <ul class="list">
          {roadmap.done.map((item) => <li>{item}</li>)}
        </ul>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
